nce the configuration was last saved.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>If BLACS crashes, and hence doesn't save the latest experiment queue, the next time it starts it tries to load a potentially outdated queue from the last time it was closed cleanly.\nThere should be a try/except when loading these shots into the queue on startup, as they may have been deleted since the configuration was last saved.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "new", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2018-07-11T02:26:07.269269+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2018-07-11T05:12:41.738890+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 45}